      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we actually have to wait for initialization to complete here?\n\nThe setters don\u0027t read the existing data before updating it so they don\u0027t care if it\u0027s missing.\n\nGetUploadsEnabled/GetLastUploadAttemptTime can just return 0 if the file doesn\u0027t exist.\n\nGetClientId can fall back to attempting to complete initialization of the client id file if it doesn\u0027t exist.",
